item.title: Parameters
item.description: ParametersEach client supports the following set of parameters as part of their deployment, regardless of the deployment mechanism. Most of the parameters listed below are also configurable in the Zero Trust Dashboard under Settings > Devices. In the event of conflicting settings, the WARP client will always give precedence to settings on the local device (for example, in your mdm.xml or com.cloudflare.warp.plist files). ​â€‹ Required for full Cloudflare Zero Trust features For the majority of Cloudflare Zero Trust features to work, you need to specify a team name.
